				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="gdlist">
				<img class="img-responsive checkout" src="images/checkout.png"/>
				<div class="dbimg">
					<img class="img-responsive" src="images/gb5.png" alt="" />
				</div>
				<div class="det">
					<h5>小雏菊鲜花 家庭插花 厂家直发</h5><span class="tj">[店长推荐]</span>
					<div class="optnum">
						<div class="optnumdec left">-</div>
